==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: gracilariid
<hw>gracilariid</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>Any of several small dull or
metallic-colored tineoid moths whose larvae mine in plant leaves; a
member of the <fam>Gracilariidae</fam>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> gracilariid moth.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gracilariidae</ent>⟦br⟧
